  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2019-10-17",
    "date": "2019-11-14T21:36:02Z",
    "text": "Davis-Bacon Repeal Act\n\n This bill repeals the Davis-Bacon Act (which requires that the locally prevailing wage rate be paid to various classes of laborers and mechanics working under federally-financed or federally-assisted contracts for construction, alteration, and repair of public buildings or public works).\n\nReferences in any law to a requirement under the Davis-Bacon Act shall be null and void."
  },
